title: Remove a testing artifact that should have been deleted
body:
### Context

@rokonec noticed that there was this new console testing artifact that somehow snuck its way in when I made https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/pull/8503. That's a bit embarrassing! We should really remove it. There's no dependency on this/these file(s).

commit.message: Remove a testing artifact that should have been deleted
